metadata.name: Vitrase 6200 USP U 5mL Injection powder lyophilized for solution

clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For increase of absorption and distribution of other injected drugs and for rehydration

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Hyaluronidase hydrolyzes hyaluronic acid and increase diffusion of injected drugs thus facilitating their absorption Hyaluronidase is used for enhancing absorption and distribution of other injected drugs
